::Zardus/Reptilica/DevilDuer::

Zardus enters the lab, looking at the femm on the table. "Allright, your 
presence isn't required," he says to Reptilica and DevilDuer, dismissing them.

"Hey, boss, don't forget to make her a slut!" DevilDuer says as the two walk 
out, leaving Zardus and the femm. Zardus takes a seat on a chair, opening 
Feline's face plate. Attatching a few wires, he turns to a comp, begining to 
type.
